  "_comment_screenshots": "Re-enable the screenshots[] block below once screenshots/{today,calendar,plan,money,cornileus}.png exist. They were referenced but not yet committed — manifest validators flag missing screenshot URLs and Chrome's install UI silently falls back to text-only.",
